title: Kaweenakumik Islands Ecological Reserve
text: Kaweenakumik Islands Ecological Reserve is an ecological reserve located on several islands in <a href="Lake%20Kaweenakumik">Lake Kaweenakumik</a>, <a href="Manitoba">Manitoba</a>, <a href="Canada">Canada</a>. It was established in 1989 under the Manitoba <a href="Ecological%20Reserves%20Act">Ecological Reserves Act</a>. It is in size.
